{
  "stem": "14251.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These are simple needs, but they are necessary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they would bring you back to their space during the day--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in the morning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'd go in there in my nightgown.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the idea was, if something did happen to them, I would be found up there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nobody would know that I was a Jewish child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How were they going to know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wouldn't be in the same attic space.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mentioned that we actually were in a flat, and the rooms were allocated to people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You didn't have your whole flat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember there was a woman with blond hair.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I even still remember her hair and all because it was so unusual to see Jewish people with blond hair.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even to us it was unusual, even though I had the blond hair.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But my parents didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother's sister and all these people didn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, this woman's name was Trudchen-- which means Little Trudy-- Traploviz I can find her name now in the black book of all the dead German Jews, in the two volumes that I have.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It has about 340,000 names in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Trudchen Traploviz, I believe, is the one who jumped out of the window when they came to arrest them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In other words, they would come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There would be that dreaded knock after 7:00 at night, and you knew somebody is being rounded up, Since this was not just our place to live but of a number of others, it could be for someone else.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when that happened, I understand that, like so many people, one was arrested, the other one jumped out the window.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the attic, banging on the doors-- no, there were no doors in the attic, but one steel door.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
